I think it will be a headache. Eventually we have to face the need for
updated AUMF with flexibility and oversight, but no idea how to get there
in a smart and effective way, especially in the current environment. may
want to drop it here so we can give it more in-depth focus later rather
than opening a can of worms with no plan.




